{"id":205034,"date":[{"year":1950,"month":11,"day":25}],"page":"7","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"美术周刊","column":"","genre":"","count":"107","ytitle":"","mtitle":"打气和泄气","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>何基</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1950\\11\\50bp070901.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>美帝军阀在部队中进行色情文化和宗教麻醉，说是为了给士兵打气。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1950\\11\\50bp070902.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>又鼓励屠杀、奸淫、掠夺，驱使少爷兵们上了朝鲜战扬，说也是为士兵打气。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1950\\11\\50bp070903.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>但失掉人性，思想愈趋堕落的美国士兵，一遇朝鲜人民军，士气便完全泄了。</FONT>"}]}